        <problem>
          <para>You are given a test tube that contains a mixture of iron filings and sulphur. You are asked to weigh the amount of iron in the sample.</para>
          <list list-type="enumerated">
            <item>
              <para>Suggest one method that you could use to separate the iron filings from the sulphur.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
              <para>What property of metals allows you to do this?</para>
            </item>
