        </problem>
        <problem>
          <para>Given the following descriptions, write the chemical formula for each of the following substances:</para>
          <list list-type="enumerated">
            <item>
              <para>silver metal</para>
            </item>
            <item>
              <para>a compound that contains only potassium and bromine</para>
            </item>
            <item>
              <para>a gas that contains the elements carbon and oxygen in a ratio of 1:2</para>
